{"tid":854675,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世]入NGO之前真係要諗清楚","createTime":"2018-10-09T14:04:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T14:18:49.000Z","uid":84768,"like":35,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"81212bbb9b15e9b221225597e3614070445c6ece","tid":854675,"uid":84768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T14:04:30.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟最近因多左幾千蚊一個月轉左去間ngo到做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我個位係類似文員加一個監察嘅角色，上一份工都係paper work比較多，有時監察下生產線，屌下d細有咩位做得唔啱咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，咁interview個陣，個manager講嘅duty同我原本個份都差不多，咁多幾千就即刻狗衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講埋福利，可能有巴絲唔太清楚，ngo係乜7福利都無，無bonus 無13個月，淨係得基本6次medical (200蚊內拎單去claim )同10日al咁，我入職前都知所以唔緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁呢幾日翻新工去fam下，去其他team實習下，隔離team都有我呢個位，做做下就發現唔對路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，根本同我原先工作嘅野唔同，要落埋生產線做加完全唔係做關於監察嘅野而差不多無任何paper work，其他team呢個位個d師兄又柒下柒下任鳩過manager點去做d唔係自己位應做嘅野，佢地仲覺得咁做係理所當然。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我認我on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 貪每個月多幾千走去做雜工，而家已經搵緊工，拎埋呢個月糧就即quit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後奉勸各位巴絲簡ngo之前真係要諗清楚，佢可以話自己係ngo唔夠人之後掉你去做d完全唔關你工作範疇嘅野，三思呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd8b440c77cdff233ea12ba3637b47c7b791d07","tid":854675,"uid":2998,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T14:27:50.000Z","msg":"得10日al，你個間ngo好細？<br />\n一般都15al up"},{"pid":"5776f6a3a1f0956ad02d59f52b25aec3387b8da0","tid":854675,"uid":196625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T14:45:18.000Z","msg":"生產線? 咩工黎"},{"pid":"bcab34f20e509c6995dc3759bb4f6c4a7beb221d","tid":854675,"uid":38456,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T14:4